{"tid":1769683,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[瀨屎系列] Outlast 又出新一集啦","createTime":"2019-12-05T05:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:45:47.000Z","uid":67454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9a49bb8788bbf40b853c9937b2e871ddfd4d924a","tid":1769683,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRc73x4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRc73x4.jpg&h=3843fe9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRed Barrels 表示，他們很高興向玩家公開《絕命精神病院》世界中最新作品，<span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲設定在冷戰時代，玩家將面對在冷戰時的恐怖人體實驗</span>。<br />\n<br />\n《絕命精神病院實驗》並非《絕命精神病院》前兩集的續作，而是採用同一個世界觀，<span style=\"color: red;\">為單人或多人合作遊戲，玩家將扮演實驗的受害者，除了可以獨自遊玩面對外，也可選擇與其他至多三個被迫成為實驗對象的玩家合作遊玩</span>，而目前研發團隊尚未公開玩家到底將面臨何種恐怖情境。<br />\n<br />\n從首度公開的宣傳海報看到玩家似乎將可以在遊戲中運用夜視鏡，但實際內容如何，仍將等待研發團隊未來公布。《絕命精神病院實驗》目前仍在研發初期階段，尚未公開遊戲平台與上市時程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實現實可能仲恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8689f92131205ab2703758047683a6c75c332b07","tid":1769683,"uid":192813,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"第一隻最正<br />\n第二隻不了"},{"pid":"20d161c9b9160b3900094e2beb6538511333a44e","tid":1769683,"uid":81995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"睇幅圖以為出 vr <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8342b12147a16db8d25ab1e6eeb89cace0f88a","tid":1769683,"uid":117265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20d161c9b9160b3900094e2beb6538511333a44e","tid":1769683,"uid":81995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T05:16:40.000Z","msg":"睇幅圖以為出 vr <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T05:17:48.000Z